# ── Build output (regenerated by PyInstaller from the .spec) ─────────────
/Pak-Rat.exe
/_internal/
/build/
/dist/
/_release/

# ── Release archives — host these as GitHub Release assets, not in-tree ──
*.zip

# ── Third-party tooling — NOT shipped in source ─────────────────────────
# repak, texconv, the injector's bundled Python, and especially the
# proprietary Oodle DLL (oo2core_*.dll, RAD/Epic — not redistributable).
# The working copies live inside the release archive; see README "Building"
# for how to obtain them when building from source.
/vendor/
Pak-Rat/vendor/
oo2core_*.dll

# ── Bulky generated data we don't ship in source ────────────────────────
Pak-Rat/data/assets.txt

# ── Python caches ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# ── PyInstaller intermediates ───────────────────────────────────────────
*.spec.bak
*.toc
*.pkg
warn-*.txt
xref-*.html

# ── Editor / OS cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
